 \lim_{T\to\infty}\frac{1}{2T}\int_{-T}^T \mathrm{e}^{i\lambda x}\,dx 
 \frac{1}{2T}\int_{-T}^T \mathrm{e}^{i\lambda x}\,dx=\frac{1}{2T}\frac{1}{i\lambda} \big(\mathrm{e}^{i\lambda T}-\mathrm{e}^{-i\lambda T}\big)=\frac{\sin(\lambda T)}{T}\to 0. 
